The second donkey slaughterhouse has been opened in Naivasha.Star Brilliant is located in Kinamba trading centre, 10km from Naivasha town. It has a capacity of slaughtering more than 200 donkeys every day.Naivasha subcounty veterinary officer Miriam Nakeel praised the management for the high standards of production. The Kenya Veterinary Association has said donkey numbers have decreased as they are targeted by slaughterhouses.